BT Investment Management
							Institutional


























 
 







 
 











Investment Capability
We manage investment strategies for financial institutions including industry and corporate superannuation funds, public sector funds, sovereign wealth funds, insurance companies, endowment funds and not-for-profits organisations. Servicing over 50 institutional clients across a range of investment solutions, our focus is on long-term partnerships, with our oldest mandate dating back to 1980. We offer strategies within and across asset classes and geographies, including:

Australian Equities
Income & Fixed Interest 
Sustainability Strategies
Australian & Global REITS
Global Equities
Diversified Strategies







Our Approach & Capabilities

Whether enhancing or creating a new strategy within and across asset classes, we have structured our business to deliver tailored and objectives-based solutions. As a pure funds management business, we offer direct access to some of the most highly regarded portfolio managers in the industry with support of a dedicated innovation team and highly specialised investment boutiques.
Find out how







