BT Investment Management Limited - Profile Company Report Australia
30 September 2016 | 10 pages







Overview

	BT Investment Management Limited (BTIM) is an Australian publicly listed company that provides investment management services. BT Investment Management Limited is listed on the ASX under the code BTT; it employs approximately 150 people and is headquartered in Sydney.

	BT Investment Management Limited (BTIM) operates as a provider of investment management services to both institutional and individual clients in Australia and the UK.

	BTIM offers investment products and strategies in the following areas,


		Australian Equities

		Income & Fixed Interest

		Sustainability Strategies

		Australian & Global REITS

		Global Equities

		Diversified Strategies


	Its products include,


		BT Wholesale Monthly Income Plus Fund

		BT Concentrated Global Share Fund

		BT Wholesale High Growth Fund

		BT Wholesale Moderate Fund

		BT Whole sale MidCap Fund

		BT Wholesale Focus Australian Share Fund

		BT Pure Alpha Fixed Income Fund

		BT Wholesale Fixed Interest Fund

		BT Global Emerging Opportunities Fund – Wholesale

		BT Wholesale Imputation Fund

		BT Wholesale Enhanced Cash Fund

		BT Wholesale Managed Cash Fund

		BT Wholesale Core Global Share Fund

		BT Wholesale Global Property Securities Fund

		BT Wholesale Smaller Companies Fund

		BT MicroCap Opportunities Fund

		BT Balanced Equity Income Fund

		BT Defensive Equity Income Fund

		BT Dynamic Global Equity Fund

		BT Sustainable Conservative Fund

		BT Wholesale Asian Share Fund

		BT Wholesale Australian Sustainable Share Fund

		BT Wholesale Ethical Share Fund

		BT Wholesale International Share Fund

		BT Wholesale Japanese Share Fund

		BT Wholesale Property Investment Fund







